(29, 2, 1, 'Our Motto', 'our-motto', 'Untabbed', 'Our motto', '', '<h3 style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 22px; padding-bottom: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><b>OUR MOTTO:</b>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">CARITAS: CHARITY</span></span></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">On becoming bishop, Father Lavigerie took the motto \"Caritas\" and as his episcopal coat of arms, a pelican. The Pelican is a bird which feeds its young with its own blood.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">His life illustrated the motto and coat of arms he had chosen. Arriving in Algiers, he addressed the Muslim Algerians: \"I claim the privilege of loving you like sons \" At the bishop\'s house he welcomed orphans and he founded two missionary societies to help them - the Missionaries of Africa (White Fathers) and the Missionary Sisters of Our Lady of Africa (White Sisters). He required from their members the same compassion that he himself had towards the Africans. \"For our love to bear fruit, we must see Our Lord Himself in the patients we care for and in those touched by our charity and our patience\"(Lavigerie).</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Mother Marie Salome and charity&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Our first superior general, Mother Marie Salom, invited the Sisters to live \"this charity in its twofold objective: God and neighbour.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(101, 101, 101); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;I would like to see it become, so to speak, the passion of our apostolic life and seize everything within us, our thoughts, our desires, above all our heart, to turn everything to this single aspiration: to love God and neighbour. \"</p>');
INSERT INTO `menu_sub_sub` (`cmenu_id`, `menu_id`, `sub_menu_id`, `cmenu_name`, `cmenu_url`, `page_type`, `cmenu_header`, `page_picture`, `page_content`) VALUES
(30, 3, 2, 'Friends of the gathering', 'friends-of-the-gathering', 'Untabbed', 'Friends of the gathering', '', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\"Whatever you did to one of my little ones, you did to me.\"&nbsp;</em><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">This Gospel sentence is the motto of my service in the Foyer de l\'Enfance, in the capital of Mauritania - Nouakchott.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Foyer de l\'Enfance is a day care and rehabilitation center for children with disabilities.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">It is the first facility of this type in the country.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">In Foyer de l\'Enfance I have been working for three years with a team of 8 people: nuns and lay people.</font></font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">In the morning, children are transported by bus from all parts of the city, often up to 30 km away.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Our morning greeting is a celebration as if we haven\'t seen each other in a long time.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">During the next meetings during the day, the children also show joy, they never get tired of it - as if it was the first meeting each time.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">These moments are like the Magnificat, full of joy.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">After greeting and breakfast, children start artistic activities, physiotherapy and play.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Our pupils are divided into three groups - according to age and degree of disability.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">A group of older children work in the room with sister Ignatia.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">With the help of their parents, they make artistic works, learn their names and recognize numbers.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">A group of younger children and toddlers meet in a large hall.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Older, after a few minutes of singing (with which we start each day),&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">apart from discovering the beauty of the world through artistic works, they exercise their abilities and mind while having fun.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The youngest have their own corner, where we try to stimulate them with toys in front of a large mirror</font></font><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">and properly selected exercises.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">After one hour of classes, the children are massaged by their mothers.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">This is a special time when mother pays full attention to her little daughter or son.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">One of our goals is to show mums how to work with their babies.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">This happens under the supervision of a physiotherapist who has been working</font></font><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">in the Center for a year and who selects exercises according to individual needs.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The joy of every success, work or exercise is always great, which constantly amazes me.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">As I write this short testimony, I see a boy named Usman who died a few weeks ago.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">He neither walked nor spoke, but expressed his feelings with his eyes and facial expressions.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">He had a beautiful smile, and his gaze showed gratitude.</font></font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">For a child, a trip to the Center is an important event, because it involves a toilet, wearing clean clothes, driving through the city, having a meal and - most importantly - meeting other children and having fun.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Parents often tell us about their children crying when, for various reasons, they cannot come to classes.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Disabled children staying at home have less attention from others, less activities and, above all, they cannot meet other children.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Many</font></font><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">of them are still deprived of medical care, and those who live in cities, unfortunately, are often used as \"bait\" for begging.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">They spend the whole day in a wheelchair, at a crossroads or in front of some important office, waiting for alms from people passing by.</font></font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Every day we have more and more children in the Center, especially little ones.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">One</font></font><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">of the main causes of disability in this area is getting married</font><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">within the same family circle.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">Another reason is perinatal complications and hereditary diseases.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">In the Center we also have handicapped children due to complications after malaria or other diseases.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">The lack of a care system for the disabled means that mothers who have sought help in all other institutions come to us as a last resort, hoping that we will help heal their children.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">It is a big challenge for our entire team to support these mothers in hope every day</font></font><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">and how to discover together with them that a handicap does not have to be an obstacle in their relationship with each other, in achieving the fullness of life, but on the contrary - that a child\'s illness can be a blessing for the whole family.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">As I greet all of you, I entrust to your prayers these children and their mothers, as well as our entire team.&nbsp;</font><font style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\">God bless you!</font></font></p>'),
